**Recommendation:** Conduct user testing specifically measuring whether players are motivated by "I want to learn this" vs "I want crystals/streaks." If the latter dominates, reduce crystal earn rates and increase narrative rewards. See Section 10.
**‚ö†Ô∏è Gap:** We use Kaplan as the source but haven't verified if our AI extraction captures 100% of testable concepts. Some nuanced application scenarios in Kaplan that require multi-paragraph context may be lost in micro-segmentation. Need a "concept coverage audit" against AAMC content outline.
